### Expense Distribution by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/distribution
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expense Distribution (with date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/distribution?from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Monthly Trend
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/monthly?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Daily Trend
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily?from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
